Class AddModify_AppointmentController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controllers.AddModify_AppointmentController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class AddModify_AppointmentController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Used to add and edit appointment records. Called from the main screen this screen is both the add screen and the edit screen. Certain fields are loaded by the calling screen using static variables in this file.

      • onClick_Save

        public void onClick_Save​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
        Handles the click on the save button. Before saving the following validations are performed in this method: Validate Both Contact and Customer are Selected. Validate that this customers appointment doesn't overlap any other appointments for that customer. Validate that the appointment time is chronologically before the end time. Then it saves the appointment and closes the screen.
        Parameters:
        actionEvent - - required parameter for button click
